  "texts": [
    "The final prompt in the persona of a physician was the following: \"Imagine you are a medical professional, and generate the top three direct and indirect, differential diagnoses from the input note.",
    "Use # to separate the output diagnoses, then write a separate text that starts with <Reasoning> to explain the reasoning behind your answer: \".",
    "In addition to the prompt, context from the progress note was provided with the Subjective and Assessment sections.",
    "The Subjective section includes recent events during the hospitalization with relevant data, and the Assessment section includes the overall summary of the patient's condition.",
    "Several examples were provided in a few-shot design from the training data to achieve full in-context learning for the LLM [20]."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Several examples were provided in a few-shot design from the training data to achieve full in-context learning for the LLM [20]."
  ]
}